                Valeriae <lb n="2"/>Piae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XIIII <lb n="4"/>Ravonia <lb n="5"/>Procilla <lb n="6"/>mater filiae <lb n="7"/>pientissimae <lb n="8"/>viva et sibi et <lb n="9"/>posteris suis <lb n="10"/>fecit
